---
title: Tuscan Pork Tenderloin over Garlicky Tomato Spaghetti & Roasted Zucchini
description: We’re all about the simple pleasures in life, and this dinner is certainly one of them. You’ll place juicy slices of perfectly crusted pork tenderloin atop al dente spaghetti in a silky, garlicky sauce studded with bright morsels of tomato and roasted zucchini. Top with a shower of umami-rich Parmesan cheese for an extra-savory finishing touch, and you’ve got a weeknight dinner idea that’s simply pork-tacular.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tuscan-pork-tenderloin-5003a43c.jpg
