  sodium: 510 mg
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/tuscan-pork-tenderloin-6419b3f5246bc509830727f3
servings: 2
author: Michelle Doll Olson
cuisine: Mediterranean
